-- Portuguese Secretary of State for Energy Gomes Resigns
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-03-13T07:37:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/portuguese-secretary-of-state-for-energy-gomes-resigns.html
Henrique Gomes,  Portugal ’s
secretary of state for energy, said he has decided to step down
from the government.  Gomes cited “personal and family” reasons for his
decision to resign, according to a statement e-mailed late
yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henrique Almeida in Lisbon at 
